            <title>[PIG-2142] Allow registering multiple jars from DFS via single statement</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2142</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Pig currently allows users to register jars from local and remote filesystems, but only one jar can be specified at a time. It would be great to be able to say something along the lines of &quot;register hdfs://user/me/lib/&lt;b&gt;lucene&lt;/b&gt;.jar&quot; and get all the jars registered in one go.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
